nodes.text: Nazish was a Rishii Zulirian Swordmistress. She was one of only three individuals to have mastered the aerial sword combat known as Trispzest. Although the other two individuals, Maw and Kharys used a lightsaber with this technique, as a Zulirian Swordmistress, it is likely that Nazish used a simple blade in place of a lightsaber.
